item.title: CVE-2017-14586|2024-08-05T19:34:38.504Z -- atlassian -- hipchat%20for%20mac%20desktop%20client
item.description: The Hipchat for Mac desktop client is vulnerable to client-side remote code execution via video call link parsing. Hipchat for Mac desktop clients at or above version 4.0 and before version 4.30 are affected by this vulnerability.
